						               													<description>Are you ready to embark on a magical adventure filled with cute little critters and powerful potions?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Come and join the fun with WitchDraft, the exciting new card game that immerses you in the world of young witches and their adorable animal helpers. In WitchDraft you become a student and you will draft the ingredients needed to create the most potent potion, while enlisting the help of your little animal friends to collect the necessary components.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;WitchDraft is an engaging card game with charming artwork that immerses you in the world of young witches learning the art of potion-making. Through a draft mechanic that encourages strategic decision-making, both skill and intuition are key.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;WitchDraft is a game that's sure to delight both young and old alike. Explore the enchanting world of WitchDraft, where magical creatures and powerful potions await!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Do you have what it takes to become a master potion-maker with WitchDraft?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay:&amp;#10;The game plays over 2 rounds. Each player will draw a recipe and  an ingredients scoring card and keep them secret from other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the start of each round, each player draws 4-6 cards, depending on the player count.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn each player will choose 1 of those cards and put them in their open card display in front of them. They will have to carefully choose the position and rotation of the card to maximize their potion. This position is locked then.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After that each player will give all remaining cards to the left player and choose 1 card again until all cards are chosen.&amp;#10;After 2 rounds of play each player will count their collected brew points by referencing to their recipe and ingredients scoring card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player with the most brew points has created the most potent potion and is declared winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
